    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/ceb83ed1a52cb45c6faec3460738eaf4.poster.avif?t=1759166460\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/ceb83ed1a52cb45c6faec3460738eaf4.webm?t=1759166460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/ceb83ed1a52cb45c6faec3460738eaf4.mp4?t=1759166460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/3ced2e9c6d79e993d1fbbb893a3d730a.avif?t=1759166460\" width=618 height=70 /></span>特兰顿家族的古老诅咒，迫使年轻的苏珊小姐踏上一段危机四伏的旅程。她将在通往真相的途中，邂逅来自冥界的灵魂，结识盟友，也将面对敌人—— 只为揭开那场毁灭她整个家族的真正凶手之谜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/d2a5fa91df37059354a0b0c23c165c39.poster.avif?t=1759166460\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/d2a5fa91df37059354a0b0c23c165c39.webm?t=1759166460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/d2a5fa91df37059354a0b0c23c165c39.mp4?t=1759166460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/c74c575e2743cea6063e1f2fdb61801b.avif?t=1759166460\" width=618 height=70 /></span>很久以前，在特兰顿家族那座历经岁月洗礼的古堡中，一对恩爱的夫妇迎来了他们的女儿。 她的名字叫苏珊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >苏珊的父亲格林先生，是一位风度翩翩、极具影响力的绅士，深受家人敬爱。然而某天，他突然离奇身亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >母亲阿加莎陷入悲痛，日日如幽魂般在空旷的城堡中游荡。 亲友不忍她沉沦，便劝她再婚，嫁给一位沉稳富有的绅士——奥斯汀先生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生活似乎重新步入正轨。奥斯汀成为了一家之主，掌控着阿加莎和年幼的苏珊。然而，这样的平衡并未维持太久。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仿佛有某种诅咒，正随着一只黑猫的脚步悄然蔓延，罪恶也随之而来……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/a5dcb593e8e6c2010989b3c381f4b84c.poster.avif?t=1759166460\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/a5dcb593e8e6c2010989b3c381f4b84c.webm?t=1759166460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/a5dcb593e8e6c2010989b3c381f4b84c.mp4?t=1759166460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/815372cbe56bb3341c4098d2a7f49b97.avif?t=1759166460\" width=618 height=70 /></span>《秘密城堡》是一款剧情驱动的心理悬疑冒险游戏。你将置身于一个令人毛骨悚然却又优雅美丽的 3D 世界，与风格鲜明的 2D 手绘角色进行互动，步步深入谜团之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>谜题与剧情紧密交织</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个谜题不仅仅是挑战，更是通向真相的关键线索。 你的每一次解答，都会左右故事的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3D点击式探索体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由穿梭于古堡的每一个阴影角落，收集、分析并组合物品，揭开隐藏其中的黑暗秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30多位错综复杂的角色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一场邂逅都充满变数。有人伸出援手，有人暗藏杀机，每个人都有自己的目的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多分支剧情与多个结局</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的选择将塑造苏珊小姐的命运。你，是否已经准备好面对一切？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式原创手绘艺术风格</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从细腻的 3D 场景，到独具个性的 2D 手绘角色，每一个细节都经过精心打磨，构筑出一个艺术与诡秘交织的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/268461bd6d16d186943c0bc8e153b22a.poster.avif?t=1759166460\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/268461bd6d16d186943c0bc8e153b22a.webm?t=1759166460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825110/extras/268461bd6d16d186943c0bc8e153b22a.mp4?t=1759166460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
